title: Daz3d - Poser - RDNA - EVI-B05 - Space Defenders: Earth Force Co
description:
Swiped from another site which I won't mention.  Uploaded here since it looked interesting.

Descritpion: Earth Force Command is the first line of defense against alien invaders. This bundle contains all of our Earth Force Command outfits for V4. The Communications Officer keeps all of the ships in Earth orbit in contact with each other and Earth Force Headquarters. The Commander manages the crew of her ship, negotiates with hostile aliens, and when all else fails, engages them in battle. The Nurse keeps the troops healthy and fixes them up when they get injured in battle. The Lieutenant serves on the front lines, directing battles and repelling boarders. The Admiral is in charge of coordinating Earth Force's fleet of ships. The Security Officer maintains order onboard ships and is the last line of defense against boaders.

Features:
- All outfits contain all applicable CrossDresser adjustment morphs for easy posing.
- Some outfits have movement and/or fitting morphs
Product Includes:
- Earth Force Command Communications Officer
- Earth Force Command Commander
- Earth Force Command Nurse
- Earth Force Command Lieutenant - Earth Force Command Security Officer
- Earth Force Command Admiral 

Reference link: http://www.runtimedna.com/Space-Defenders-Earth-Force-Command-V4-Bundle.html
